<h6 id="toc0"><span><strong><em>&quot;If ya' ain't livin' life to it's fullest, than I reckon ya' ain't livin' at all.&quot;</em></strong></span></h6>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:smaller;">– Ulysses B. Donkman</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<h5 id="toc1"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4768">SCP-4768 - The Tall Tales of Ulysses B. Donkman</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc2"><span><em>The Man, The Myth, The Article that Started it All.</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<h3 id="toc3"><span>Foundation Donkuments</span></h3>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<h5 id="toc4"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5307">SCP-5307 - Double Donk Juice</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc5"><span><em>A mysterious stranger, musical vape juice, and just a little more than meets the eye.</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="toc6"><span>Tallest Tales:</span></h3>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9b/Train_Icon_bw.svg" style="height:75px; width:75px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc7"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-clockwork-bandits">Ulysses B. Donkman and the Clockwork Bandits</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc8"><span><em>Donkman's up against some bolted bandits in this rootin' tootin' romp of train heist gone wrong!</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="http://kontainer.djkakt.us/local--files/the-funeral/1582572222984.png" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc9"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-heinous-hitman">Ulysses B. Donkman and the Heinous Hitman</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc10"><span><em>Impossible! Donkman, have you really met your end?</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="http://topia.wikidot.com/local--files/collab:ravenmilk/bicon" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc11"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-mournful-birthday">Ulysses B. Donkman and the Mournful Birthday</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc12"><span><em>Even Donkman has his somber days, that don't mean there ain't time to play the hero.</em></span></h6>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#FFF8E7; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><img src="http://topia.wikidot.com/local--files/collab:ravenmilk/fishicon" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc13"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-foreboding-forest">Ulysses B. Donkman and the Foreboding Forest, Pt. 1</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/the-donkman-s-den/cavecon" style="height:75px; width:70px; padding-left: 0%;" /></p>
<h5 id="toc14"><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ulysses-b-donkman-and-the-foreboding-forest2">Ulysses B. Donkman and the Foreboding Forest, Pt. 2</a></strong></span></h5>
<p><strong>Written By: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721425" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span></strong></p>
<h6 id="toc15"><span><em>Donkman finds out what real fear tastes like.</em></span></h6>
</div>
